::Hevngjerrig::
       He walks over to Maxima slowly.  He reaches out and brushes her chin 
with his hand.  "What's the matter, don't you like it?"  He smiles in both an 
outward, cocky manner, and a private, inward manner.  "Or did you prefer me 
with the stench of goodness?"

--part1_14.101f45b3.2be09e97_boundary
